Author: CrisF#3405
Content: Could you tell me how I can use `swap ID` and find out txids for the trade?

Author: artem.pikulin#0794
Content: @CrisF Click on particular swap on `History` page and you will see this screen:

Author: artem.pikulin#0794
Content: However it displays payments tx id/hashes only and doesn't display spends.

Author: artem.pikulin#0794
Content: If you're using MM2 CLI you may get full swap status with all transactions details by calling `my_swap_status`: https://developers.atomicdex.io/basic-docs/atomicdex/atomicdex-api.html#my-swap-status
